OL,3,CITV News speaks to pole vault champion
OL,4,Cafter GB win three golds in 30 minutes
OL,6,FPole vault gold medallist Molly
OL,7,FCaudery has told ITV News that her win
OL,8,Fon Sunday is a result she will
OL,9,F"absolutely cherish forever."
OL,11,FMs Caudery was the only woman to clear
OL,12,F4.85m in the pole vault at the World
OL,13,FIndoor Athletics Championships in
OL,14,FPoland.
OL,16,FHer win came amid a hat-trick of gold
OL,17,Fmedals for Great Britain on Sunday,
OL,18,Fwhen Team GB picked up three gold
OL,19,Fmedals in under 30 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
