OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774357890
OL,3,CITV News speaks to pole vault champion
OL,4,Cafter GB win three golds in 30 minutes
OL,6,FAlongside Molly Caudery, the two other
OL,7,Fmedals went to Georgia Hunter Bell in
OL,8,Fthe 1500m, and Keely Hodgkinson in the
OL,9,F800m.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, the 26-year-old
OL,12,Fpole vaulter said, "I know my younger
OL,13,Fself would be so proud.
OL,15,F"For me, Keely and Georgia, to be
OL,16,Fthere together and inspiring the next
OL,17,Fgeneration, it's so special."
OL,19,FITV News spoke to Molly Caudery
OL,20,Ffollowing her success on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
