OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774357890
OL,3,CITV News speaks to pole vault champion
OL,4,Cafter GB win three golds in 30 minutes
OL,6,FMolly had previously won the title in
OL,7,FGlasgow two years ago, but what
OL,8,Ffollowed her success was a shock
OL,9,Fqualifying exit at the Paris Olympics
OL,10,Fin 2024 and an ankle injury in the
OL,11,Fwarm-up at last year's World
OL,12,FChampionships.
OL,14,FJust six weeks ago, Molly was still
OL,15,Fstruggling with returning to pole
OL,16,Fvaulting.
OL,18,F"Physically, I was in good shape, but
OL,19,Fmentally that was the issue. I really,
OL,20,FI couldn't take off. I was scared of
OL,21,Fthe pole vault.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774357890
OL,3,CITV News speaks to pole vault champion
OL,4,Cafter GB win three golds in 30 minutes
OL,6,F"I had this fear in me that I've never
OL,7,Fhad before, and that is really hard to
OL,8,Fkind of overcome.
OL,10,F"I had to work really closely with my
OL,11,Fcoach to figure a lot of things out,
OL,12,Fbut it's made me so much stronger.
OL,14,F"I'm so excited going into summer
OL,15,Fknowing what I can do and how much I
OL,16,Fcan progress in six weeks."
OL,18,FSix weeks ago, Molly was struggling
OL,19,Fwith returning to pole vaulting
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
