OL,3,CITV News speaks to pole vault champion
OL,4,Cafter GB win three golds in 30 minutes
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShortly before Caudery's win, Georgia
OL,12,FHunter Bell secured her own first
OL,13,Fglobal gold in the 1500m.
OL,15,FMinutes later, Keely Hodgkinson
OL,16,Fachieved gold in the 800 metres final,
OL,17,Ffinishing in one minute 55.3 seconds.
OL,19,FHodgkinson later returned to the track
OL,20,Fto run the anchor leg in the women's
OL,21,F4x400m relay final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
